Package: inferCSN
Type: Package
Title: Inferring cell-specific gene regulatory network
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2023-04-10
Author: MengXu
Maintainer: The package maintainer: MengXu <mengxu98@qq.com>
Description: A method for inferring cell-specific gene regulatory network from single-cell transcriptome data.
    We will continue to add other omics data in the future work.
URL: https://mengxu98.github.io/inferCSN/
